testSpeech.py
================

Testing code for Text to Speech functionality using espeak utility.

Run testSpeech.py by typing "python testSpeech.py" in your RPi terminal.

Note: To force the Audio to 3.5 mm jack headset, use "sudo raspi-config", Goto Audio session in Advanced Settings, choose Force 3.5mm option. Otherwise the audio will be routed through HDMI port.

main_subscribe_speech.py
===================

Connect to internet first. and run the code using "python main_subscribe_speech.py",
Connect a headset in 3.5 mm jack and listen to it.
Push some data to "myspeak" topic using MQTT Dashboard Application. The data send should be spoken out through the speaker.